description: This beautifully updated floor-through, upper duplex condo lives like a single-family home!  Located just steps from the beach, parks, public transportation, and more, this gem is an opportunity you don’t want to miss.  Upon entering, you’ll be welcomed by a bright, sunny, open-concept living space, perfect for entertaining. Enjoy the luxury of a deck and private roof deck access right off the dining area, offering outdoor space and stunning views. The spacious kitchen is a chef’s dream, featuring expansive cabinetry, S/S appliances, granite countertops, and a walk-in pantry. You’ll also find a convenient half bath on this floor, a large living area with a cozy fireplace, and plenty of natural light. The gorgeous hardwood floors flow seamlessly into the second level, adding warmth and character. Upstairs, you’ll find two generously sized bedrooms offering ample closet space.  This is more than just a condo—it’s a lifestyle. Schedule your private showing today!
